le/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1661%2C1107 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2214%2C1476 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Frameset details\" title=\"Vielo\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Vielo-715ed7b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The V+1’s frameset looks clean and elegant.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Vielo</i></span></p></div><p>The new bikes feature a lower bottom bracket, shorter seat tube and longer top tube, bringing the rider lower and further forward for a racier position and lower centre of gravity.</p><p>While not as extreme as some on the market, Vielo’s <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/sizing-and-fit/road-bike-geometry-explained/\">geometry</a> could certainly be called progressive for gravel.</p><p>A size medium has 393mm of reach favouring fairly short stems, while the stack of 572mm is middling to low for gravel, in keeping with the bike’s racy intentions.</p><p>Along with a reasonably slack 70.5mm head angle, the medium’s wheelbase is a lengthy 1,057mm, suggesting it won’t be too flighty on rough terrain.</p><h3>Vielo V+1 geometry and sizing</h3><p>Vielo has done away with the dropped chainstay design and gone symmetrical instead, but has still managed to increase tyre clearances.</p><p>With a new and supposedly stiffer fork as well, there’s now apparently room for 700×50mm or 650×50mm tyres at both ends.</p><p>The new bike’s head tube now sports a fashionable – and potentially more aero – hourglass shape.</p><p>Each frame option comes in two paintjobs and we’re pleased to report that <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/enough-with-the-black-bikes-already/\">none are boring black</a>.</p><p>The best news of all is Vielo has retained the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/features/bikes-with-fender-mounts/\">mudguard (fender) mounts</a> making the bike all the more appealing for year-round all-road antics.</p><h2>Vielo V+1 specs and pricing</h2><h3>V+1 Alto</h3><ul><li><strong>Frameset:</strong> £3,899</li><li><strong>SRAM Force Mullet build:</strong> £6,299</li><li><strong>Shimano GRX Di2 build:</strong> £5,999</li></ul><h3>V+1 Strato</h3><ul><li><strong>Frameset:</strong> £3,399</li><li><strong>Campagnolo Ekar build:</strong> £5,699</li><li><strong>Shimano GRX mechanical build:</strong> £4,799</li></ul></section></div>","author":"Matthew Loveridge","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"c8e4b27b02c394631615182d1cd28bd503b31ec523889069ea331dd61fd5cfe0","category":"Cycling"}